lence from a bank that combines specialist expertise and outstanding service with an international presence etc but over and above these strengths it is doubtless our banks human dimension and its individual approach to managing its staff that will make you want to work with us distinctive valuesaside from our commitment to the values intrinsic to our profession such as confidentiality and ethics indosuez wealth managements teams share several more distinctive valuespersonal commitment and a sense of responsibility an entrepreneurial spirit that is part of a collective dynamic dedication to others and respect  these are the foundations of indosuez wealth managements culturethese values are very much alive they are applied by each person in their work and are shared with new recruits they are also promoted via crossbusiness initiatives such as our corporate social responsibility which is focused on respect and by our philanthropy helping each individual pursue their own personal excellence and encouraging talentin line with its values indosuez wealth managements ambition is to provide individual support to each of its employees and to help them realise their full potential encouraging each person to progresseach member of staff is supported over time taking into account their specific situation and their career path our bank offers individual or collective career development programmes to identify appropriate opportunities a motivating compensation policywe offer a motivating competitive compensation package adjusted to the different activities and the financial markets and rounded out by an attractive benefits policy a variety of career development opportunitiesin addition to the international opportunities offered by the banks crossbusiness structure there are also opportunities to transfer to other activities including those available in crédit agricole group all members of staff who follow this path are given personal and global support ensuring collective developmentindosuez wealth management pays special attention to the development of each individual and simultaneously works to ensure all of its employees are part of the group dynamic indosuez wealth management regularly organises collective events such as seminars for staff responsible for client relations management development programmes or initiatives for staff showing strong potential nurturing team spiriteach persons talent and their capacity to take the initiative are crucial to our pursuit of excellence but we are convinced we can do even more together this is why our managerial culture gives priority to coconstruction over isolated work in particular via a flexible team model focused on each client we ensure that the assigned objectives are shared throughout the team in the same vein we combine local responsibility with a crossbusiness dimension print indosuez our international reach an avid explorer of new horizons our  specialist entities around the world are a safehaven of knowhow and expertise group profile our way of doing things at indosuez wealth management our way of doing things is defined by our own story and the stories that have shaped who we are today as well as by our human dimension our sense of responsibility and perspective group profile responsible by nature responsibility is one of the core values that make us who we are it governs our activities our relationships with our clients and our colleagues and much more careers apply indosuez wealth management is growing and wants to grow more it has many opportunities for both experienced professionals and those starting out in their careers to find out about our opportunities visit our online recruitment website careers students for us teaching means something careers graduates a commitment between you and us careers experienced professionals your talent could make all the difference to our future careers our businesses and its people a unique combination of expertise sharing the same vocation care