djust the structure of your assets with the assistance of our wealth structuring specialistswealth structuring teams comprised of specialists in the global structuring of family private or business assets in order to optimise their ownership management and transfer taking into account the tax regime applicable to each clientcorporate finance teams who assist with entrepreneurs equity transactions and certain investments in unlisted companiescomplex credit structuring teams who essentially focus on business assets or specific real estate investmentsphilanthropy teams who assist with the selection of projects and provide support for personal initiatives a panoramic view indosuezs structuring wealth professionals come from diverse cultural backgrounds and are able to find expert answers to even the most complex wealth questions taking on board the international dimension and going beyond purely financial matterstheir expertise is enhanced by our crossbusiness structure which carries out permanent monitoring and exchange of information at an international level fostering an indepth understanding of legal and fiscal risks indosuez wealth management takes an exhaustive global approach assetliability management privatebusiness wealth profitnonprofit structures etc to help you continue to build and extend your wealth  print wealth management architects of wealth see our approach to helping clients ensure their legacy lasts through a trilogy of highlyspecialised services group profile our way of doing things at indosuez wealth management our way of doing things is defined by our own story and the stories that have shaped who we are today as well as by our human dimension our sense of responsibility and perspective who we help families helping to protect and grow your fortune generate income and pass on your wealth who we help entrepreneurs  corporate executives wealth management solutions to structure both your personal and professional assets who we help institutions specialised solutions allowing you to concentrate on your own business who we help ultrahigh net worth individuals indosuez wealth management has the expertise needed to build the bespoke solutions some of our clients expect indosuez insights indosuez insights check out our mobile app get industryleading insights from indosuez wealth management on your mobile structuring wealth for the private sphere protecting growing and preparing to pass on your wealth is above all about taking care of the ones you love  the most important thing there is structuring wealth for business matters if you are invested in a business as an entrepreneur shareholder or executive manager the management of your wealth must factor in this dimension careers artisans of excellence like master craftsmen the men and women of indosuez wealth management are driven by their shared pursuit of excellence our bank actively aids them in this pursuit by means of its identity and human resources initiatives back to top because of the international dimension of indosuez wealth management users are informed that they may be asked to visit the websites of indosuez wealth management entities located in different countries users are urged to review the terms and conditions appearing on the pages of each of the entities each entity operates in compliance with the applicable laws and regulations and the licenses that it has users are advised that indications about services and products are provided for informational purposes only and cannot be considered as constituting an offer or solicitation users are also advised that the mentioned services and products may not be provided by all the entities and may be restricted for certain persons or residents of certain countries read and approved to continue on the site and make browsing easier please enable cookies they allow us to a remember your usage preferences display settings and the media players that you use b develop anonymous statistics number of visits to the web