s to fully understand the product and provide them with full transparency this can only be achieved with a limited numberhe added with a volatility of  per cent and an annualised performance of  per cent since  this fund which is one of the very few fund of hedge funds registered for sale in the netherlands provides an excellent opportunity for investorsgreen way arbitrage is a luxembourgregistered fund of hedge funds sicav specialising in arbitrage strategies it invests across selected low volatility strategies such as fixed income arbitrage equity  risk arbitrage index arbitrage and market neutral equities and is aimed at investors looking to make lower volatility investment into alternatives in order to diversify their portfolios minimum investment is euros commenting on future plans for the benelux region mr detobel said we obviously have plans to launch new products in the benelux and elsewhere in europe but only by tailoring or packaging them following local demand and requirements green way arbitrage can also be sold in luxembourg as it is a luxembourg sicavbackground note crédit agricole alternative investment products group caaipg a subsidiary of crédit agricole asset management is one of the leading global players in alternative investments with over  years experience and around euros  billion under management in funds of hedge fundscaaipg operates out of four locations  paris london chicago and tokyo caaipgs clients include institutional investors banks for own account or thirdparty and distributorscrédit agricole asset management is the asset management company for the crédit agricole group it carries out investment management activities from seven centres paris london milan madrid tokyo hong kong and singapore at  september  assets under management amounted to euros  billion crédit agricole asset managements customers include french and foreign institutional investors and individual investors through the groups network and through distribution agreementsin addition to its development in france crédit agricole asset management plans to continue with its international expansion by strengthening its existing network of subsidiaries and representative offices in europe germany spain italy sweden and belgium and in japan asia and the uscrédit agricole asset management has been assigned an aa intrinsic rating by fitch amr for all its management operations and has aimrpps and gips certificationcrédit agricole asset managements investment policy results from a general policy that favours active management underpinned by rigorous investment processes that systematically include risk monitoring like this article  get the free daily newsletter print email furtherreading from hedgeweek hfr reports hedge funds allocations beat redemptions thu    optima chief defends hedge funds of funds wed    lyxor reports hedge fund performance recovers in february mon    skybridge capital sells majority stake with anthony scaramucci to step down immediately tue    hedge funds showing improved performance for  tue    from our other sites hedge fund launches down and liquidations up reports hfr fri    preqin reports seven months of positive returns for hedge funds thu    man group’s results hit by difficult markets tue    what current trends tell us about the future of the hedge fund industry mon    avoiding the funerals has kept veteran firm on the survival list mon    features guides  guide to setting up an alternative investment fund in europe wed   blogs before you head to the beach… fri   the cftc provides more robust protection to whistleblowers wed   awards hedgeweek global awards  thu   special reports cybersecurity in europe  wed   mitigating compliance risk for pe managers thu   sei blockchain  building ecosystems in financial services fri   mifid ii meeting the compliance challenge sat   investment opportunities in infrastructure debt thu   cayman alternative investment summit  wed   events total alts thursday september     catalys